        <div type="letter">
            <div type="text">
                <opener>
                    <placeName>Stanhope St.</placeName>
                    <date>28 Feby.1826</date>
                    <salute>My dear Sir</salute>
                </opener>
                <div type="transcription">
                     
                  <p>I send you a report which shows we are still creeping on - Bankes was asked yesterday by Sir Sandford Graham whether he meant to go to the Poll, &amp; he said that nothing but Death should prevent him from doing so; If I do not said he you may set me down as a Liar. This I think good news.</p>
                  <p>My dear Sir</p>
                  <p>Yrs sincerely</p>
                  <p>Palmerston</p>
                  <p>I have just been presenting the University Petition about Colonial Slavery &amp; have expressed my full &amp; entire concurrence with its sentiments</p> 
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
        
